truetype-tracer (4.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Display the extents of the string and its final X advance in
    a comment, in order to help with assembling multiple strings.
  * Allow an XY offset to be set at the beginning of a string.
    [many thanks to John Kasunich for these two changes]
  * export biarcs for dxf [thanks to Jeff Epler]
  * export splines/nurbs for gcode
  * optional filling of characters with -l 

 -- Chris Radek <chris@timeguy.com>  Sun, 13 Jun 2010 13:24:26 -0500

